Adrenogamer <protoman@firemail.cc>

WHAT IS THAT
This folder contains Binder IPC subsystem driver: binder_filter source code,
adopted source code for different platforms and patches for patching binder,
Kconfig and Makefile for any kernel.

CONTENTS
rootdir contains binder_filter source code for device flo
'vanilla' directory contains patch files.

SOURCE CODE STRUCTURE
binder IPC code:		 	 drivers/staging/android/binder.c
binder_filter must be paste here	 drivers/staging/android/binder_filter.c
					 drivers/staging/android/binder_filter.h
Kconfig and Makefile for Binder		 drivers/staging/android/Makefile
 					 drivers/staging/android/Kconfig
 
PATCHING SOURCE CODE
1. Copy/paste binder_filter.h, binder_filter.c to your kernel source code:

cp <path-to-BinderFilter-project>/BinderFilter/src/binder_filter.c <path-to-kernel-source>/drivers/staging/android/
cp <path-to-BinderFilter-project>/BinderFilter/src/binder_filter.h <path-to-kernel-source>/drivers/staging/android/

2. Apply patches for your binder.c, Kconfig and Makefile:

cp <path-to-BinderFilter-project>/BinderFilter/src/vanilla/*.patch <path-to-kernel-source>
patch -p1 < binder.patch
patch -p1 < Makefile-binderfilter.patch
patch-p1 < Kconfig-binderfilter.patch

